text.section:
The following books and records shall be maintained by the State Law Library:
All copies of Volumes 1 to 77 of the Kentucky Reports;
Twenty-five (25) copies each of Volumes 78 to 314 of the Kentucky Reports;
Two (2) sets of all future publications of the journals and nine (9) sets of the Acts of the General Assembly; and
Two (2) sets of the official Kentucky statute publications.
